---
// Spectre Browser — landing page
// Built with Astro. Deploy to any static host.
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Spectre — Browse Without a Trace</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Spectre is a privacy-first browser built on Chromium with tracking protection, fingerprint resistance, zero telemetry, and a curated extension store." />

  <meta property="og:type"        content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url"         content="https://koels.site/spectre" />
  <meta property="og:title"       content="Spectre — Browse Without a Trace" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="A Chromium-based browser with strict tracking protection, fingerprint resistance, zero telemetry, and a curated extension store — all on by default." />
  <meta property="og:image"       content="https://koels.site/og.png" />
  <meta property="og:image:width"  content="1200" />
  <meta property="og:image:height" content="630" />
  <meta property="og:site_name"   content="Spectre Browser" />
  <meta property="og:locale"      content="en_US" />

  <meta name="twitter:card"        content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title"       content="Spectre — Browse Without a Trace" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="A Chromium-based browser with tracking protection, fingerprint resistance, and zero telemetry — on by default." />
  <meta name="twitter:image"       content="https://koels.site/og.png" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:       #05050f;
      --bg2:      #08081a;
      --surface:  rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
      --surface2: rgba(255,255,255,0.065);
      --border:   rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --border2:  rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
      --text:     #eeeeff;
      --muted:    rgba(238,238,255,0.52);
      --dim:      rgba(238,238,255,0.28);
      --cyan:     #00ccff;
      --cyan2:    #66deff;
      --violet:   #7b5fff;
      --green:    #00e87a;
      --red:      #ff4560;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      position: relative;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.028) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    nav, main, footer, .stats-strip, .policy-section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    /* ─── NAV ─── */
    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 2.5rem;
      height: 56px;
      background: rgba(5,5,15,0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .logo {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .logo-dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--cyan);
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--cyan), 0 0 16px rgba(0,204,255,0.4);
    }

    .nav-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.75rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .nav-gh {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.38rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-gh:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--text); }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 9rem 1.5rem 7rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 1000px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 35%,
        rgba(0,204,255,0.11) 0%,
        rgba(123,95,255,0.07) 40%,
        transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.28rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 99px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,204,255,0.22);
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.06);
      color: var(--cyan2);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
    }

    .badge-pulse {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--cyan);
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--cyan);
      animation: blink 2.4s ease infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.25; }
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.045em;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    }

    .hero h1 .line-ghost {
      display: block;
      color: transparent;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px rgba(238,238,255,0.18);
    }

    .hero h1 .line-solid { display: block; }

    .hero h1 .accent {
      background: linear-gradient(100deg, var(--cyan), var(--cyan2) 60%, #aaf0ff);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* ─── DOWNLOAD ─── */
    .download-wrap {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #008ab5, #00ccff 80%);
      color: #010a0f;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
      box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(0,204,255,0.28), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      position: relative;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 40px rgba(0,204,255,0.42), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }

    .btn-primary:active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .btn-primary.soon {
      background: var(--surface2);
      color: var(--muted);
      box-shadow: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      cursor: not-allowed;
      opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .btn-primary.soon::after {
      content: 'builds in progress';
      position: absolute;
      top: -22px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--cyan);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .platform-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-platform {
      padding: 0.38rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--dim);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-platform:hover { border-color: var(--border2); color: var(--muted); }

    .btn-platform.active {
      border-color: rgba(0,204,255,0.35);
      color: var(--cyan);
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.07);
    }

    .platform-hint {
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    /* ─── STATS STRIP ─── */
    .stats-strip {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg2);
      overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .stat {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 160px;
      max-width: 260px;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .stat-value {
      display: block;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .stat-value.c { color: var(--cyan); }
    .stat-value.g { color: var(--green); }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    /* ─── SECTIONS ─── */
    .section {
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 2.75rem;
    }

    /* ─── BENTO ─── */
    .bento {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.6rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; right: 0;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(0,204,255,0.055), transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,204,255,0.22);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
    }

    .c2 { grid-column: span 2; }
    .c3 { grid-column: span 3; }

    .card-icon {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card-body {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .card-body code {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.82em;
      color: var(--cyan2);
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    }

    .card-chip {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--cyan);
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,204,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 0.18rem 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    /* ─── EXTENSION STORE SECTION ─── */
    .store-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .ext-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }

    .ext-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,204,255,0.2);
      background: var(--surface2);
    }

    .ext-icon {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .ext-info { min-width: 0; }

    .ext-name {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .ext-desc {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .store-note {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,204,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .store-note strong { color: var(--text); }

    /* ─── PRIVACY POLICY ─── */
    .policy-section {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .policy-inner {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .policy-inner h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .policy-updated {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--dim);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .policy-block {
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .policy-block:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      padding-bottom: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .policy-block h3 {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
    }

    .policy-block p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .policy-block a { color: var(--cyan2); text-decoration: none; }
    .policy-block a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    .footer-outer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

    footer {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer-logo .logo-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; box-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--cyan); }

    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.75rem; }

    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .footer-copy { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--dim); }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .c2, .c3 { grid-column: span 6; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      nav { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 6rem 1.25rem 5rem; }
      .stats-strip { flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .stat { min-width: 50%; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .footer-links { gap: 1.25rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ─── NAV ─── -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="logo">
      <span class="logo-dot"></span>
      Spectre
    </a>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#extensions">Extensions</a></li>
        <li><a href="#download">Download</a></li>
        <li><a href="#privacy-policy">Privacy</a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://github.com/koelss/Spectre" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="nav-gh">
        ↗ GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>

    <!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
    <section class="hero" id="download">
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>

      <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-pulse"></span>
        <span id="version-badge">latest</span> — open source
      </div>

      <h1>
        <span class="line-ghost">browse</span>
        <span class="line-solid">without a <span class="accent">trace.</span></span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-sub">
        Spectre is a Chromium-based browser with tracking protection,
        fingerprint resistance, and zero telemetry — plus a curated
        extension store that actually works.
      </p>

      <div class="download-wrap">
        <a id="btn-primary" class="btn-primary" href="https://github.com/koelss/Spectre/releases/latest">
          <span id="btn-icon">⬇</span>
          <span id="btn-label">Download Spectre</span>
        </a>
        <div class="platform-row">
          <a class="btn-platform" data-platform="win"   href="https://github.com/koelss/Spectre/releases/latest">win x64</a>
          <a class="btn-platform" data-platform="linux" href="https://github.com/koelss/Spectre/releases/latest">linux x64</a>
          <a class="btn-platform" data-platform="mac"   href="https://github.com/koelss/Spectre/releases/latest">macos arm</a>
        </div>
        <span class="platform-hint" id="platform-hint">detecting platform…</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── STATS STRIP ─── -->
    <div class="stats-strip">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value g">0</span>
        <span class="stat-label">bytes of data collected</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value c">100%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">open source</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value">CRX</span>
        <span class="stat-label">extension support built in</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value">OFF</span>
        <span class="stat-label">auto-updates disabled</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── FEATURES ─── -->
    <section class="section" id="features">
      <span class="section-tag">What's different</span>
      <h2>Privacy on by default.<br />Not as a setting.</h2>

      <div class="bento">

        <div class="card c3">
          <span class="card-icon">🛡</span>
          <div class="card-title">Strict Tracking Protection</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Blocks trackers, cryptominers, social tracking scripts, and fingerprinters
            from the moment you launch — no setup, no toggle required.
          </p>
          <span class="card-chip">on by default</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card c3">
          <span class="card-icon">📡</span>
          <div class="card-title">Zero Telemetry</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            All data collection, crash reporting, and analytics are stripped out.
            There is no opt-out because there is nothing to opt out of.
          </p>
          <span class="card-chip">compiled out</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🎭</span>
          <div class="card-title">Fingerprint Resistance</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Canvas, WebGL, font, and audio fingerprinting are all spoofed or blocked
            so sites can't build a profile of your browser.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🔒</span>
          <div class="card-title">HTTPS-Only</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Every connection is forced to HTTPS. Spectre warns you before
            falling back to an unencrypted connection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🌐</span>
          <div class="card-title">DNS over HTTPS</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            DNS resolves through an encrypted resolver by default, so your ISP
            can't log every site you visit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🚫</span>
          <div class="card-title">No Google Services</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Safe Browsing, Google sync, crash reporting, and all built-in Google
            endpoints are removed from the build entirely.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🔗</span>
          <div class="card-title">WebRTC IP Leak Fix</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            WebRTC is restricted to proxy-only mode so your real IP can't be
            leaked by video or voice call sites.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🍪</span>
          <div class="card-title">Auto Cookie Clearing</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Third-party cookies are blocked and all cookies are cleared on close
            by default, keeping sessions from persisting across sites.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

